{
  "info": {
    "_postman_id": "semana3-transportista-2026",
    "name": "Semana 3 — Empresa Transportista EFS + S3",
    "description": "# Flujo en 2 carpetas secuenciales\n\n## Carpeta 1 — Negocio (video principal)\nCrear pedidos en memoria → el sistema genera el PDF → guarda en EFS + S3.\n\n## Carpeta 2 — Cloud (como el profesor)\nDemostrar ordenamiento en bucket, consulta con filtros, descarga, PUT y DELETE.\n\n**Variables:** `ec2_host`, `bucket`, `pedido_id_1`, `pedido_id_2`, `fecha`, `transportista`, `nombreGuia`, `fecha2`, `transportista2`, `nombreGuia2`",
    "schema": "https://schema.getpostman.com/json/collection/v2.1.0/collection.json"
  },
  "item": [
    {
      "name": "1. Negocio — Pedidos y Guías",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "1. POST — Crear pedido 1 (TransportesSur)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('201 Created', () => pm.response.to.have.status(201));",
                  "const body = pm.response.json();",
                  "pm.collectionVariables.set('pedido_id_1', body.id);",
                  "pm.collectionVariables.set('fecha', body.fecha);",
                  "pm.collectionVariables.set('transportista', body.transportista);"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"cliente\": \"Maria Lopez\",\n  \"direccion\": \"Av. Libertad 123, Santiago\",\n  \"descripcion\": \"Caja mediana fragil\",\n  \"transportista\": \"TransportesSur\",\n  \"fecha\": \"20250604\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "http://{{ec2_host}}:8080/api/pedidos",
              "protocol": "http",
              "host": ["{{ec2_host}}"],
              "port": "8080",
              "path": ["api", "pedidos"]
            },
            "description": "Crea PED-001. Key futura: 20250604/TransportesSur/guia-PED-001.pdf"
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "2. POST — Generar guía pedido 1",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('201 Created', () => pm.response.to.have.status(201));",
                  "const body = pm.response.json();",
                  "pm.collectionVariables.set('nombreGuia', body.nombreGuia.replace('.pdf', ''));",
                  "pm.collectionVariables.set('fecha', body.fecha);",
                  "pm.collectionVariables.set('transportista', body.transportista);"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "http://{{ec2_host}}:8080/api/pedidos/{{pedido_id_1}}/generar-guia",
              "protocol": "http",
              "host": ["{{ec2_host}}"],
              "port": "8080",
              "path": ["api", "pedidos", "{{pedido_id_1}}", "generar-guia"]
            },
            "description": "El sistema genera el PDF y lo guarda en EFS y S3. Sin subir archivo manual."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "3. POST — Crear pedido 2 (TransportesNorte)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('201 Created', () => pm.response.to.have.status(201));",
                  "const body = pm.response.json();",
                  "pm.collectionVariables.set('pedido_id_2', body.id);",
                  "pm.collectionVariables.set('fecha2', body.fecha);",
                  "pm.collectionVariables.set('transportista2', body.transportista);"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [{"key": "Content-Type", "value": "application/json"}],
            "body": {
              "mode": "raw",
              "raw": "{\n  \"cliente\": \"Carlos Pino\",\n  \"direccion\": \"Calle Norte 456, Valparaiso\",\n  \"descripcion\": \"Documentos urgentes\",\n  \"transportista\": \"TransportesNorte\",\n  \"fecha\": \"20250605\"\n}"
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "http://{{ec2_host}}:8080/api/pedidos",
              "protocol": "http",
              "host": ["{{ec2_host}}"],
              "port": "8080",
              "path": ["api", "pedidos"]
            },
            "description": "Crea PED-002 en otra carpeta: 20250605/TransportesNorte/"
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "4. POST — Generar guía pedido 2",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('201 Created', () => pm.response.to.have.status(201));",
                  "const body = pm.response.json();",
                  "pm.collectionVariables.set('nombreGuia2', body.nombreGuia.replace('.pdf', ''));"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "http://{{ec2_host}}:8080/api/pedidos/{{pedido_id_2}}/generar-guia",
              "protocol": "http",
              "host": ["{{ec2_host}}"],
              "port": "8080",
              "path": ["api", "pedidos", "{{pedido_id_2}}", "generar-guia"]
            },
            "description": "Segunda guía en carpeta distinta: 20250605/TransportesNorte/guia-PED-002.pdf"
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "5. GET — Listar pedidos",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('200 OK', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "pm.test('hay 2 pedidos', () => pm.expect(pm.response.json().length).to.eql(2));"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "http://{{ec2_host}}:8080/api/pedidos",
              "protocol": "http",
              "host": ["{{ec2_host}}"],
              "port": "8080",
              "path": ["api", "pedidos"]
            }
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "6. GET — Obtener pedido 1",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('200 OK', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "pm.test('guia generada', () => pm.expect(pm.response.json().guiaGenerada).to.eql(true));"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "http://{{ec2_host}}:8080/api/pedidos/{{pedido_id_1}}",
              "protocol": "http",
              "host": ["{{ec2_host}}"],
              "port": "8080",
              "path": ["api", "pedidos", "{{pedido_id_1}}"]
            }
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "name": "2. Cloud — Ordenamiento EFS + S3",
      "item": [
        {
          "name": "1. GET — Listar todo el bucket",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('200 OK', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "pm.test('al menos 2 objetos', () => pm.expect(pm.response.json().length).to.be.at.least(2));"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "http://{{ec2_host}}:8080/s3/{{bucket}}/objects",
              "protocol": "http",
              "host": ["{{ec2_host}}"],
              "port": "8080",
              "path": ["s3", "{{bucket}}", "objects"]
            },
            "description": "Inventario completo: ves las 2 keys con orden fecha/transportista/archivo.pdf"
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "2. GET — Consultar guías TransportesSur",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('200 OK', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "pm.test('total = 1', () => pm.expect(pm.response.json().total).to.eql(1));"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "http://{{ec2_host}}:8080/s3/{{bucket}}/consulta?fecha={{fecha}}&transportista={{transportista}}",
              "protocol": "http",
              "host": ["{{ec2_host}}"],
              "port": "8080",
              "path": ["s3", "{{bucket}}", "consulta"],
              "query": [
                {"key": "fecha", "value": "{{fecha}}"},
                {"key": "transportista", "value": "{{transportista}}"}
              ]
            },
            "description": "Solo guías de 20250604/TransportesSur/"
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "3. GET — Consultar guías TransportesNorte",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('200 OK', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "pm.test('total = 1', () => pm.expect(pm.response.json().total).to.eql(1));"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "http://{{ec2_host}}:8080/s3/{{bucket}}/consulta?fecha={{fecha2}}&transportista={{transportista2}}",
              "protocol": "http",
              "host": ["{{ec2_host}}"],
              "port": "8080",
              "path": ["s3", "{{bucket}}", "consulta"],
              "query": [
                {"key": "fecha", "value": "{{fecha2}}"},
                {"key": "transportista", "value": "{{transportista2}}"}
              ]
            },
            "description": "Solo guías de 20250605/TransportesNorte/"
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "4. GET — Descargar guía pedido 1",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": ["pm.test('200 OK', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));"],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "GET",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "http://{{ec2_host}}:8080/s3/{{bucket}}/object?fecha={{fecha}}&transportista={{transportista}}&nombreGuia={{nombreGuia}}",
              "protocol": "http",
              "host": ["{{ec2_host}}"],
              "port": "8080",
              "path": ["s3", "{{bucket}}", "object"],
              "query": [
                {"key": "fecha", "value": "{{fecha}}"},
                {"key": "transportista", "value": "{{transportista}}"},
                {"key": "nombreGuia", "value": "{{nombreGuia}}"}
              ]
            },
            "description": "Descarga el PDF generado por el sistema. Guardar como archivo para el PUT si lo necesitas."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "5. POST — Subir PDF externo (ruta propia)",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": ["pm.test('201 Created', () => pm.response.to.have.status(201));"],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "POST",
            "header": [],
            "body": {
              "mode": "formdata",
              "formdata": [
                {"key": "file", "type": "file", "src": [], "description": "Cualquier PDF desde tu computadora"},
                {"key": "fecha", "value": "{{fecha}}", "type": "text"},
                {"key": "transportista", "value": "{{transportista}}", "type": "text"},
                {"key": "nombreGuia", "value": "{{nombreGuiaExterna}}", "type": "text"}
              ]
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "http://{{ec2_host}}:8080/s3/{{bucket}}/object",
              "protocol": "http",
              "host": ["{{ec2_host}}"],
              "port": "8080",
              "path": ["s3", "{{bucket}}", "object"]
            },
            "description": "Sube un PDF externo con nombre y ruta propios. No reemplaza guia-PED-001.pdf. Key: fecha/transportista/documento-externo.pdf en EFS + S3."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "6. PUT — Actualizar guía pedido 1",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": [
                  "pm.test('200 OK', () => pm.response.to.have.status(200));",
                  "pm.collectionVariables.set('nombreGuia', pm.collectionVariables.get('nombreGuia') + '-actualizado');"
                ],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "PUT",
            "header": [],
            "body": {
              "mode": "formdata",
              "formdata": [
                {"key": "file", "type": "file", "src": [], "description": "PDF descargado en paso 4 o cualquier PDF"},
                {"key": "fecha", "value": "{{fecha}}", "type": "text"},
                {"key": "transportista", "value": "{{transportista}}", "type": "text"},
                {"key": "nombreGuia", "value": "{{nombreGuia}}", "type": "text"}
              ]
            },
            "url": {
              "raw": "http://{{ec2_host}}:8080/s3/{{bucket}}/object",
              "protocol": "http",
              "host": ["{{ec2_host}}"],
              "port": "8080",
              "path": ["s3", "{{bucket}}", "object"]
            },
            "description": "Actualiza la guia del pedido 1: renombra a guia-PED-001-actualizado.pdf, elimina la anterior en EFS y S3. Queda 1 archivo de guia en cada lado."
          },
          "response": []
        },
        {
          "name": "7. DELETE — Eliminar guía pedido 2",
          "event": [
            {
              "listen": "test",
              "script": {
                "exec": ["pm.test('204 No Content', () => pm.response.to.have.status(204));"],
                "type": "text/javascript"
              }
            }
          ],
          "request": {
            "method": "DELETE",
            "header": [],
            "url": {
              "raw": "http://{{ec2_host}}:8080/s3/{{bucket}}/object?fecha={{fecha2}}&transportista={{transportista2}}&nombreGuia={{nombreGuia2}}",
              "protocol": "http",
              "host": ["{{ec2_host}}"],
              "port": "8080",
              "path": ["s3", "{{bucket}}", "object"],
              "query": [
                {"key": "fecha", "value": "{{fecha2}}"},
                {"key": "transportista", "value": "{{transportista2}}"},
                {"key": "nombreGuia", "value": "{{nombreGuia2}}"}
              ]
            },
            "description": "Elimina la segunda guía en EFS y S3. Tras el 204, verifica en la consola S3 que el objeto ya no aparece y en la EC2 con `ls ~/efs/{{fecha2}}/{{transportista2}}/` que el PDF ya no está (las carpetas padre pueden quedar vacías)."
          },
          "response": []
        }
      ]
    }
  ],
  "variable": [
    {"key": "ec2_host", "value": "52.45.88.121"},
    {"key": "bucket", "value": "tu-bucket-guias", "description": "Nombre de tu bucket S3 (igual que AWS_S3_BUCKET)"},
    {"key": "pedido_id_1", "value": "PED-001"},
    {"key": "pedido_id_2", "value": "PED-002"},
    {"key": "fecha", "value": "20250604"},
    {"key": "transportista", "value": "TransportesSur"},
    {"key": "nombreGuia", "value": "guia-PED-001"},
    {"key": "fecha2", "value": "20250605"},
    {"key": "transportista2", "value": "TransportesNorte"},
    {"key": "nombreGuia2", "value": "guia-PED-002"},
    {"key": "nombreGuiaExterna", "value": "documento-externo"}
  ]
}
